## Active Challenges and Open Loops

<!-- What's actually weighing on you right now — both concrete blockers and things occupying background mental space. Pepper surfaces these in your morning brief and notices when they've been sitting too long. Update whenever something resolves or something new comes up. -->

- [Concrete challenge with status — e.g. "rental property repairs overdue, haven't called contractor"]
- [Pending task with deadline — e.g. "haven't filed Q1 estimated taxes, deadline April 15"]
- [Difficult thing being avoided — e.g. "need to have a conversation with [name] about [situation]"]
- [Background worry — e.g. "need to figure out what to do about mom's living situation"]
- [Unresolved situation — e.g. "that conversation with [colleague] that went sideways — still unresolved"]
- [Long-deferred item — e.g. "should probably get a will done"]

